# FreeBASIC source tree rsync excludes
#
# These patterns keep generated build, staging, packaging, and log content out
# of isolated worktrees and bootstrap source archives. Re-importing those
# trees can recursively copy previous staging results into new builds and
# waste large amounts of disk space.

.*
*.install_manifest
*.log
*.tmp
bin/fbc*
bootstrap/fbc*
dist/
out/
package-root/
package-root*/
packages/
pkgroot/
pkgroot*/
stage/
